
= barcodescanner


== Description

Retrievee barcode value from barcode image file

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install barcodescanner


== Features/Problems

=== Require Libraries

ImageMagick, zebra(http://zebra.sourceforge.net/)

==== install zebra

if you install zebra to non-x machine, 

	./configure --without-gtk --withouut-qt

and make, make install.

== Synopsis

	require 'rubygems'
	require 'barcodescanner'
	
	# take from test
	expected = '9784087204254'
	result = BarcodeScanner.process_image_file("#{expected}.jpg")
	assert_equal(expected, result)

=== "cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory "

	echo "/usr/local/lib" >> /etc/ld.so.conf
	/sbin/ldconfig

